# Project rules

## Language

The application language is **English**. Any Turkish text in the codebase or UI must be converted to English.

## After code changes

When any update is made to the software:

1. **Git**: Push the changes to git.
2. **Deployment**: At the end of the work, state clearly if anything must be done on **Supabase** or **Vercel** (e.g. new env vars, migrations, redeploy).
